originalText.text: Dr. Sallerson & the office staff bring a welcoming, positive vibe the minute you walk in through their door. I’ve visited their office four times and each and every time Dr Sallerson takes the time to inform you, advise you on your options & tells you what you will experience after the procedure. They make going to see your dentist pleasurable.

originalText.text: Dr. Sallerson is extraordinary! I had my first visit today and the whole experience was top notch. He’s so knowledgeable, friendly, personable and fun. (A fun dentist?) My treatment was so easy and thorough. I had a Zoom whitening and was made to be comfortable with a TV and a really comfortable, reclined dentist chair. I was checked on regularly and it went fast. The office staff is amazing. Can’t recommend enough.

originalText.text: Dr. Sallerson is the best! He is very easy to have a conversation with about treatment and makes you feel comfortable. He let’s you ask all the questions you need and will listen. I have been seeing Dylan for the last four years and I wouldn’t want another dentist. He has put inlays and onlays and my restorations look and feel amazing. He doesn't try to sell you anything. He is trustful and loyal and will only fix what’s broken. I highly recommend!
